trans-unit.source: Provides a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en skrivebeskyttet samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The TransformerTypeCollection class represents a read-only collection of objects, typically used by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> objects to manage sets of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TransformerTypeCollection representerer en skrivebeskyttet samling objekter, vanligvis brukes av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>objekter til å administrere tegnsett <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses a TransformerTypeCollection collection to keep a list of available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects on a page, whereas a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> object uses a TransformerTypeCollection collection to track the available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects that it contains.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen bruker en TransformerTypeCollection samling beholde en liste over tilgjengelige <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objekter på en side, mens en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>objektet bruker en TransformerTypeCollection samling til å spore de tilgjengelige <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objekter som den inneholder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Although the TransformerTypeCollection collection is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Selv om TransformerTypeCollection-samlingen er skrivebeskyttet, kan du endre programmatisk egenskapene for de underliggende kontrollene det refereres til i samlingen.

trans-unit.target: Kopierer samlingen til en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> collection, a subset of those objects, or a superset of those objects.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CopyTo er nyttig når du ønsker å sette sammen en egendefinert matrise kan inneholde alle de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objekter i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection>samling, et delsett av disse objektene og overordnet objektene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.TransformerTypeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>
